channel.title: <3 Homestar Runner <3
channel.description:
(i have no explanation for the hearts other than the fact that homestar is... loveable :|)
In the year 2003 when i started playing rs (i was in the seventh grade), Homestar [homestarrunner.com] was a big hit and outranked runescape on ratings based on Websearch Rankings. Now its falling waaay behind and I'm just telling everyone that even though homestar is neglected (sp?) over the ages its still something worth viewing. :(
